Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.63,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.99,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Mommy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:34.06,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,My Mother's Face
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:36.26,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.32,0:24:57.16,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Test Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:57.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Our country’s first manned exploratory space rocket, the Lion, was launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:04.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,However, 72 seconds after liftoff…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the liquid fuel booster suddenly exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And although the Space Control Center activated what could be called its self-destruct system…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the flight suspension system did not function correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:24.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The Lion fell into an urban area and caused a huge disaster with many civilian casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Five years later…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.50,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about Kamogawa's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:53.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,They said she was in that condition for five years!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:56.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It really surprised me to see her like that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It seems like it has been difficult on the father as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.78,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Going to work and the hospital all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.14,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,But I really feel sorry for Asumi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She was all alone at home this whole time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:11.73,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ever since she could remember, she never had the chance to experience her mother’s love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.61,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yes. But she's a little bit of a strange child, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now then, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Say goodbye to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what she smelled like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Smelling a dead person like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She's not a normal child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, you go back to your room for a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.04,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Were you always lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Does it not hurt anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:24.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's no fair for them to fly into the sky to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,He's going against the good of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Have a good day, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right. You be careful on your way, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:48.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot my crayons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be doing art in third period.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Let’s all draw pictures of our families today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:07.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You'll all have to clearly remember the faces of your families.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:10.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Your father, mother, siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Grandmother or grandfather... Any of them are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.11,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Will you be drawing your father, Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Draw your family as they are, with an honest spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Fuchuuya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:43.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa is drawing a picture of a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.88,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I think that's obviously against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:48.72,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.89,Spica - Tertiary,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's not against the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, then who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:11.28,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,So your mom is a monster, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But Sensei said to draw them as they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.87,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ehhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, that would make you the child of a monster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:21.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:22.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You guys are annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:26.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey now! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Don't let him say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Do it! Come on, don't give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Okay, return to your seats, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.06,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.36,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where do people go when they die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Let’s see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,According to stories that I've read in books...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...the soul becomes a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:08.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It crosses a large mountain,\Nheading towards a vast meadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:13.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...comes out of a deep forest, and beyond that forest is a big river called the Sanzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:29.74,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,NOTE: Japanese people believe the journey to the Sanzu river, the intermediate stage between life and death, takes place in 7 phases of 7 days each, or 49 days in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:18.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The spirit crosses the river on a boat and goes into the "other world."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:23.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Suzunari-sensei said that when people die, they become stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:29.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Well then, Mom may become a star once she crosses the Sanzu River as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.74,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it's been just about 49 days now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.91,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mom has crossed the Sanzu river yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot, another drone beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There aren't any stag beetles out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:03.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, my loss for listening to what Grandpa said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:08.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A loss in the form of three hours of wasted energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:12.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,At 600 yen an hour, a 1800 yen loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go catch some crayfish or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:34.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the Sanzu River looks sort of like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is Kamogawa doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're totally soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.63,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,There's trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, little Fuchuuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:28.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa is unconscious down by the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Please send an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My daughter is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:49.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm at the riverbed on the west side of Yuinogawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,T-minus five...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:13.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:13.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.07,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.74,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Liftoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:56.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:09.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well you see, this is the land of those without life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The land of those without life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:16.38,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's a place where only dead people can come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? Did I die, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:22.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No. You're still one step on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:27.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So you need to get back to your body as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How can I get back to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.98,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,See, there's a little path running through here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:43.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you follow this path all the way\Nto the end, there's a big river there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,People call it the Sanzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:50.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But you can't cross that river, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:54.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You need to walk along that river, in the opposite direction of the flowing water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you do that, you can get back to your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Also, there's one other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Those that are still living who wander into this world must never...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:08.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...say their own name aloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can't say my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:15.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Saying your own name in this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...means that you exist in this world, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Basically, it would mean that you actually died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not going to go back, onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:38.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have a body left to which I can return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:39.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:43.42,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Come on. If you don't get going,\Neveryone will be worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:57.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, have I met you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I just got that feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Comment: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:28.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I still haven't gotten there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm not really getting tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:25.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:31.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are,\Nbut do you suppose you could help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:33.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:38.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Could I have you take me to the other side of the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.83,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I can't see, so I can't follow the path...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt anywhere, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help you. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you hiding your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.19,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.42,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a rock over there, so watch out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:26.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Over there too! And over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's one over there too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my! If you tell me about so many, I won't be able to walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:38.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But still, you re a mysterious little child, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:42.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone else always gets quiet when they see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear what your name was, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.74,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...must never say their own name aloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Young lady, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:03.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is that right? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There's no meaning to names in this place anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Does your face hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:22.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No. It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:26.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But if you took off these bandages,\NI'm sure you'd be very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's very badly burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:35.49,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,But my face doesn't bother me since I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:37.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can't see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:43.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No. But you know, what you see with your eyes isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,After all, I can still feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It seems that something sad has happened to that little girl recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can feel her emotions shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:09.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I have two eyes, so it would be nice if I could just give you one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:10.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:20.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then you could see the pretty sky and the pretty sea and lots and lots of other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Come here for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.71,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Sit down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My art homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I have to finish drawing my picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A picture of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't do that! Sit still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:11.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I had a little girl as well, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Her name was Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder how old she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:24.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if she's been raised into a kind little girl like you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's doing all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.77,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.69,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,...must never say their own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I drew this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can have this picture I drew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're giving this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:46.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'd like to give you something in return, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:55.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then can you give me that thing you're wearing on your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:58.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This? It's a little dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's okay! Can I please have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We made it to the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can see a light on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:39.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to get this boat to move, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get out and try pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:56.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, young lady. I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:20:02.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I was very happy! You were the only one who stopped and helped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:07.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Fireflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My eyes can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:41.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:44.95,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:48.66,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:50.49,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I lied about forgetting my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.62,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm... Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:58.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Don't come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.17,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You can't cross this river, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, you keep on living!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.10,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:16.02,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Protecting me... It hurt a lot, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:18.90,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.82,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.03,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.86,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:27.95,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.63,0:21:49.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're awake, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:51.39,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing Fuchuuya-kun happened to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:59.52,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I... I met Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:04.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mom, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She smelled really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:24.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Fuchuuya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:29.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really looking at Kamogawa's picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:30.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.51,0:24:41.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Considerate of my falling into a panic, Kei-chan wants to push the red button and retire our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:43.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But I want to try my best a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:49.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I want to line up dominoes with Kei-chan and Ukita-san for the rest of the time we have left!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.61,0:24:53.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,After all, I only have one dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.32,0:24:57.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica. Test Complete.